                <h2 id="demand-management">Demand Management tables</h2>
                
                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DemandRequests</h3>
                <p>Demand requests submitted by policy or delivery teams for DDaT support.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>ReferenceNumber</code> - VARCHAR(50), unique reference (e.g., DR-2025-001)</li>
                    <li><code>ApplicantName</code> - VARCHAR(255), applicant name</li>
                    <li><code>ApplicantEmail</code> - VARCHAR(255), applicant email</li>
                    <li><code>BusinessArea</code> - VARCHAR(100), business area</li>
                    <li><code>ProposedTitle</code> - VARCHAR(120), proposed project title</li>
                    <li><code>OverviewAndBusinessNeed</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), overview and business need</li>
                    <li><code>ExpectedBenefits</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), expected benefits</li>
                    <li><code>RiskIfNotDelivered</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), risk if not delivered</li>
                    <li><code>Status</code> - VARCHAR(50), status (Draft/Submitted/Under Review/Approved/Deferred/Rejected)</li>
                    <li><code>IsSubmittedToTriage</code> - BOOLEAN, whether submitted to triage</li>
                    <li><code>TriageMeetingId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to TriageMeetings</li>
                    <li><code>ConvertedProjectId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to Projects (if converted)</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DemandRequestContacts</h3>
                <p>Points of contact for demand requests.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DemandRequestId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DemandRequests</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(255), contact name</li>
                    <li><code>Email</code> - VARCHAR(255), contact email</li>
                    <li><code>Role</code> - VARCHAR(100), contact role</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code> - DATETIME, creation timestamp</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DemandRequestPrioritisations</h3>
                <p>Prioritisation scoring for demand requests.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DemandRequestId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DemandRequests (one-to-one)</li>
                    <li><code>TotalPriorityScore</code> - INTEGER, overall priority score (out of 100)</li>
                    <li><code>PriorityTier</code> - VARCHAR(50), priority tier (Tier 1-4)</li>
                    <li><code>StrategicAlignmentTotal</code>, <code>UserImpactTotal</code>, <code>RiskUrgencyTotal</code>, <code>FeasibilityTotal</code>, <code>ValueOutcomeTotal</code> - INTEGER, category totals</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DemandRequestNotes</h3>
                <p>Notes and comments on demand requests.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DemandRequestId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DemandRequests</li>
                    <li><code>Note</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), note text</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedBy</code> - VARCHAR(255), creator</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code> - DATETIME, creation timestamp</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DemandRequestAssessments</h3>
                <p>Assessments conducted on demand requests.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DemandRequestId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DemandRequests</li>
                    <li><code>AssessmentType</code> - VARCHAR(50), type of assessment</li>
                    <li><code>AssessmentData</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), assessment data (JSON)</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DemandRequestSectionCompletions</h3>
                <p>Tracks completion status of demand request form sections.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DemandRequestId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DemandRequests</li>
                    <li><code>SectionName</code> - VARCHAR(100), section name</li>
                    <li><code>IsCompleted</code> - BOOLEAN, completion status</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DemandRequestRiskTypes</h3>
                <p>Junction table linking demand requests to risk types.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>DemandRequestId</code> - INTEGER, composite primary key part 1</li>
                    <li><code>RiskTypeId</code> - INTEGER, composite primary key part 2</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code> - DATETIME, creation timestamp</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">TriageMeetings</h3>
                <p>Triage meetings where demand requests are reviewed.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>Title</code> - VARCHAR(150), meeting title</li>
                    <li><code>StartAt</code> - DATETIME, meeting start time</li>
                    <li><code>EndAt</code> - DATETIME, meeting end time</li>
                    <li><code>IsActive</code> - BOOLEAN, whether meeting is active</li>
                </ul>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h2 id="ddt-standards">DDT Standards Management tables</h2>
                
                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DdtStandards</h3>
                <p>DDaT standards with versioning and validation rules.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>StandardUuid</code> - VARCHAR(36), UUID for standards as code</li>
                    <li><code>Title</code> - VARCHAR(500), standard title (required, unique)</li>
                    <li><code>Slug</code> - VARCHAR(500), URL-friendly slug</li>
                    <li><code>Summary</code> - VARCHAR(2000), brief summary</li>
                    <li><code>Purpose</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), purpose and rationale (markdown)</li>
                    <li><code>Criteria</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), criteria for meeting standard (JSON array)</li>
                    <li><code>HowToMeet</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), how to meet requirements (markdown)</li>
                    <li><code>Governance</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), governance information (markdown)</li>
                    <li><code>Version</code> - VARCHAR(20), semantic version (MAJOR.MINOR.PATCH)</li>
                    <li><code>Stage</code> - VARCHAR(50), lifecycle stage (Draft/Under Review/Approved/Published/Rejected/Archived)</li>
                    <li><code>IsPublished</code> - BOOLEAN, whether standard is published</li>
                    <li><code>PublishedAt</code> - DATETIME, publication date</li>
                    <li><code>LegalStandard</code> - BOOLEAN, whether this is a legal requirement</li>
                    <li><code>ValidityPeriod</code> - INTEGER, validity period in months</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                    <li><code>IsDeleted</code> - BOOLEAN, soft delete flag</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DdtStandardOwners, DdtStandardContacts</h3>
                <p>Many-to-many relationships for standard owners and contacts.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DdtStandardId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DdtStandards</li>
                    <li><code>UserId</code> / <code>Name</code>, <code>Email</code> - Owner/contact information</li>
                    <li><code>Role</code> - VARCHAR(100), role description</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DdtStandardCategories, DdtStandardSubCategories, DdtStandardPhases</h3>
                <p>Many-to-many relationships for standard categorisation and phase allocation.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DdtStandardId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DdtStandards</li>
                    <li><code>StandardCategoryId</code> / <code>StandardSubCategoryId</code> / <code>Phase</code> - Category/subcategory/phase reference</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DdtStandardValidationRules</h3>
                <p>Validation rules for standards as code.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DdtStandardId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DdtStandards</li>
                    <li><code>RuleType</code> - VARCHAR(50), type of validation rule</li>
                    <li><code>RuleDefinition</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), rule definition (JSON)</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DdtStandardVersions</h3>
                <p>Version history for standards.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DdtStandardId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DdtStandards</li>
                    <li><code>Version</code> - VARCHAR(20), version number</li>
                    <li><code>ChangeSummary</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), summary of changes</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code> - DATETIME, creation timestamp</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DdtStandardComments</h3>
                <p>Comments on standards during review process.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DdtStandardId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DdtStandards</li>
                    <li><code>Comment</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), comment text</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedByUserId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to Users</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code> - DATETIME, creation timestamp</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DdtStandardProducts</h3>
                <p>Products (approved and tolerated) for standards.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DdtStandardId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DdtStandards</li>
                    <li><code>ProductFipsId</code> - VARCHAR(50), product identifier</li>
                    <li><code>Status</code> - VARCHAR(20), status (approved/tolerated)</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">DdtStandardExceptions</h3>
                <p>Known exceptions to standards.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>DdtStandardId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to DdtStandards</li>
