                <h2 id="lookups">Lookup tables</h2>
                
                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">RiskTiers</h3>
                <p>Defines risk governance tier levels from project through to cross-government.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>Code</code> - VARCHAR(50), unique identifier (e.g., "PROJECT", "DEPARTMENT")</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(100), tier name (e.g., "Project-level risk")</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - TEXT, full definition with governance details</li>
                    <li><code>Summary</code> - VARCHAR(200), concise scope description</li>
                    <li><code>SortOrder</code> - INTEGER, hierarchical display order</li>
                    <li><code>IsActive</code> - BIT/BOOLEAN, whether tier appears in dropdowns</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="small text-muted">5 standard risk tiers seeded: Project, Programme, Portfolio, Department, Cross-government</p>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">RiskTypes</h3>
                <p>Defines risk categories with 13 standard types. Risks can be assigned multiple types via the RiskRiskTypes junction table.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>Code</code> - VARCHAR(50), unique identifier (e.g., "STRATEGY", "TECHNOLOGY")</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(100), display name (e.g., "Strategy risk")</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - TEXT, full definition with examples</li>
                    <li><code>Summary</code> - VARCHAR(200), concise one-line description</li>
                    <li><code>IsActive</code> - BIT/BOOLEAN, whether type appears in forms</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="small text-muted">13 standard risk types seeded covering strategic, operational, financial, technical, security, and other categories</p>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">ActionSources</h3>
                <p>Defines where actions originate from (risk, issue, milestone, service assessment).</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>Code</code> - VARCHAR(50), unique identifier (e.g., "RISK", "SERVICE_ASSESSMENT")</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(100), display name (e.g., "Risk", "Service Assessment")</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - TEXT, full definition with examples</li>
                    <li><code>Summary</code> - VARCHAR(200), concise one-line description</li>
                    <li><code>SortOrder</code> - INTEGER, display order in dropdowns</li>
                    <li><code>IsActive</code> - BIT/BOOLEAN, whether source appears in dropdowns</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="small text-muted">4 standard action sources seeded: Risk, Issue, Milestone, Service Assessment</p>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h2 id="users">Users and preferences</h2>
                
                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">Users</h3>
                <p>Stores user account information.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>Email</code> - VARCHAR(255), unique email address</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(200), full name</li>
                    <li><code>IsAdmin</code> - BOOLEAN, administrator flag</li>
                    <li><code>IsActive</code> - BOOLEAN, active account flag</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - audit fields</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">UserPreferences</h3>
                <p>Stores user-specific settings and preferences including preferred business areas.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>UserId</code> - INTEGER, primary key and foreign key to Users (one-to-one relationship)</li>
                    <li><code>PreferredBusinessAreas</code> - TEXT, comma-separated list of preferred business areas</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="small text-muted">Preferences automatically filter RAID index views to show items from selected business areas</p>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h2 id="reporting">Reporting tables</h2>
                
                <p>Tables supporting performance tracking, metrics, and compliance reporting.</p>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">PerformanceMetrics</h3>
                <p>Defines product performance metrics that can be tracked.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(200), metric name</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - TEXT, what the metric measures</li>
                    <li><code>Unit</code> - VARCHAR(50), unit of measurement</li>
                    <li><code>ValueType</code> - VARCHAR(20), data type (number, decimal, percentage, text)</li>
                    <li><code>IsActive</code> - BOOLEAN, whether metric is currently tracked</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">ProductMetricValues</h3>
                <p>Stores submitted values for product performance metrics.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>PerformanceMetricId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to PerformanceMetrics</li>
                    <li><code>FipsId</code> - VARCHAR(50), product identifier</li>
                    <li><code>Value</code> - TEXT, metric value (stored as text, type determined by PerformanceMetric.ValueType)</li>
                    <li><code>TargetValue</code> - TEXT, target value if applicable</li>
                    <li><code>ReportingPeriod</code> - VARCHAR(50), period this value covers (e.g., "2024-01")</li>
                    <li><code>Notes</code> - TEXT, commentary and context</li>
                    <li><code>SubmittedBy</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to Users</li>
                    <li><code>SubmittedAt</code> - DATETIME, when value was submitted</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">EnterpriseMetrics</h3>
                <p>Enterprise-level KPIs with values and targets.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(200), metric name</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - TEXT, what the metric measures</li>
                    <li><code>ValueType</code> - VARCHAR(20), data type (number, decimal, percentage, text)</li>
                    <li><code>CurrentValue</code> - TEXT, current value</li>
                    <li><code>TargetValue</code> - TEXT, target value</li>
                    <li><code>ReportingPeriod</code> - VARCHAR(50), current reporting period</li>
                    <li><code>IsActive</code> - BOOLEAN, whether metric is currently tracked</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">FunctionalStandards</h3>
                <p>DDaT functional standards definitions (may be synced from external Standards CMS).</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>StandardId</code> - VARCHAR(50), unique standard identifier</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(200), standard name</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - TEXT, standard description</li>
                    <li><code>Purpose</code> - TEXT, purpose of the standard</li>
                    <li><code>HowToMeet</code> - TEXT, guidance on meeting the standard</li>
                    <li><code>IsActive</code> - BOOLEAN, whether standard is current</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">FunctionalStandardThemes</h3>
                <p>Themes within functional standards for organization.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>FunctionalStandardId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to FunctionalStandards</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(200), theme name</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - TEXT, theme description</li>
                    <li><code>SortOrder</code> - INTEGER, display order</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">PracticeAreas</h3>
                <p>Practice areas within themes for detailed categorisation.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>ThemeId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to FunctionalStandardThemes</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(200), practice area name</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - TEXT, practice area description</li>
                    <li><code>SortOrder</code> - INTEGER, display order</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">Criteria</h3>
                <p>Individual criteria within practice areas for assessment.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>PracticeAreaId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to PracticeAreas</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(200), criterion name</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - TEXT, detailed criterion description</li>
                    <li><code>SortOrder</code> - INTEGER, display order</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">FunctionalStandardAssessments</h3>
                <p>Records of assessments conducted against functional standards.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>FunctionalStandardId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to FunctionalStandards</li>
                    <li><code>FipsId</code> - VARCHAR(50), product being assessed</li>
                    <li><code>AssessmentDate</code> - DATETIME, when assessment was conducted</li>
                    <li><code>AssessedBy</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to Users</li>
                    <li><code>OverallCompliance</code> - VARCHAR(20), overall compliance level</li>
                    <li><code>Notes</code> - TEXT, assessment notes</li>
                    <li><code>CreatedAt</code>, <code>UpdatedAt</code> - DATETIME, audit timestamps</li>
                </ul>

                <p class="small text-muted">Related tables include AssessmentCriteriaResponses for individual criterion results within each assessment.</p>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">AssessmentCriteriaResponses</h3>
                <p>Individual criterion responses within functional standard assessments.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>AssessmentId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to FunctionalStandardAssessments</li>
                    <li><code>FunctionalStandardId</code>, <code>ThemeId</code>, <code>PracticeAreaId</code>, <code>CriteriaCode</code> - Composite foreign key to Criteria</li>
                    <li><code>Response</code> - VARCHAR(50), response value</li>
                    <li><code>Evidence</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), supporting evidence</li>
                </ul>

                <hr class="my-4">

                <h2 id="enterprise-reporting">Enterprise Reporting tables</h2>
                
                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">EnterpriseReturns</h3>
                <p>Enterprise returns for reporting periods.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>Year</code> - INTEGER, reporting year</li>
                    <li><code>Month</code> - INTEGER, reporting month</li>
                    <li><code>Status</code> - VARCHAR(50), return status</li>
                    <li><code>SubmittedAt</code> - DATETIME, submission timestamp</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">EnterpriseMetricValues</h3>
                <p>Metric values within enterprise returns.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>EnterpriseReturnId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to EnterpriseReturns</li>
                    <li><code>EnterpriseMetricId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to EnterpriseMetrics</li>
                    <li><code>Value</code> - TEXT, metric value</li>
                    <li><code>TargetValue</code> - TEXT, target value</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">StaffRoleReturns</h3>
                <p>Annual GDD role returns for staff.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>UserId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to Users</li>
                    <li><code>Year</code> - INTEGER, return year (unique per user/year)</li>
                    <li><code>GddRoleId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to GddRoles</li>
                    <li><code>SubmittedAt</code> - DATETIME, submission timestamp</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">StaffRoleReturnSkills</h3>
                <p>Secondary skills for staff role returns.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>StaffRoleReturnId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to StaffRoleReturns</li>
                    <li><code>SkillId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to Skills</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">GddRoles</h3>
                <p>GDD role definitions.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>RoleFamily</code> - VARCHAR(200), role family</li>
                    <li><code>RoleName</code> - VARCHAR(200), role name</li>
                    <li><code>RoleLevel</code> - VARCHAR(50), role level</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), role description</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">Skills</h3>
                <p>Skill definitions for staff role returns.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>SkillName</code> - VARCHAR(200), unique skill name</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), skill description</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">Kpis</h3>
                <p>Key Performance Indicators for projects, objectives, and milestones.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>Code</code> - VARCHAR(50), unique KPI code</li>
                    <li><code>Name</code> - VARCHAR(200), KPI name</li>
                    <li><code>Description</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), KPI description</li>
                    <li><code>Category</code> - VARCHAR(100), KPI category</li>
                    <li><code>UnitOfMeasure</code> - VARCHAR(50), unit of measurement</li>
                    <li><code>TargetValue</code> - DECIMAL(18,4), target value</li>
                    <li><code>ProjectId</code>, <code>ObjectiveId</code>, <code>MilestoneId</code> - INTEGER, optional foreign keys</li>
                    <li><code>OwnerUserId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to Users</li>
                    <li><code>Active</code> - BOOLEAN, active flag</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">KpiDataPoints</h3>
                <p>Performance data points for KPIs.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>KpiId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to Kpis</li>
                    <li><code>ReportingPeriodStart</code> - DATETIME, period start</li>
                    <li><code>ReportingPeriodEnd</code> - DATETIME, period end</li>
                    <li><code>Value</code> - DECIMAL(20,4), metric value</li>
                    <li><code>ValueNarrative</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), narrative description</li>
                    <li><code>TargetValue</code> - DECIMAL(20,4), target value</li>
                    <li><code>SubmissionStatus</code> - VARCHAR(30), submission status</li>
                    <li><code>SubmittedByUserId</code> - INTEGER, foreign key to Users</li>
                    <li><code>SubmittedAt</code> - DATETIME, submission timestamp</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">ProductReturns</h3>
                <p>Product returns for performance reporting periods.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>FipsId</code> - VARCHAR(50), product identifier</li>
                    <li><code>Year</code> - INTEGER, reporting year</li>
                    <li><code>Month</code> - INTEGER, reporting month (unique per FipsId/Year/Month)</li>
                    <li><code>Status</code> - VARCHAR(50), return status</li>
                    <li><code>SubmittedAt</code> - DATETIME, submission timestamp</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">PerformanceReportingDueDateOverrides</h3>
                <p>Overrides for performance reporting due dates.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>ReportingYear</code> - INTEGER, reporting year</li>
                    <li><code>ReportingMonth</code> - INTEGER, reporting month (unique per Year/Month)</li>
                    <li><code>DueDate</code> - DATETIME, override due date</li>
                    <li><code>IsActive</code> - BOOLEAN, active flag</li>
                </ul>

                <h3 class="h6 mt-3">PerformanceReportingBusinessAreaConfigs</h3>
                <p>Configuration for performance reporting by business area.</p>
                <ul class="small">
                    <li><code>Id</code> - INTEGER, primary key</li>
                    <li><code>BusinessAreaName</code> - VARCHAR(200), business area name</li>
                    <li><code>IsActive</code> - BOOLEAN, active flag</li>
                    <li><code>Configuration</code> - NVARCHAR(MAX), configuration data (JSON)</li>
